OL,5,C'good'
OL,7,FLast year, 85% of the 450 bathing
OL,8,Fwaters monitored in the UK were
OL,9,Fclassed as "excellent" or "good."
OL,11,FThe government claimed the improvement
OL,12,Fin last year's figures was a result of
OL,13,Fpolicies it had introduced aimed at
OL,14,Fclearing up Britain's waters.
OL,16,FThe government said bathing water
OL,17,Fquality in England has improved
OL,18,Fdramatically since the 1990s,
OL,19,Ffollowing decades of regulation by
OL,20,Fsuccessive governments, alongside
OL,21,Finvestment and partnership work.
