OL,7,FBut 7%, some 32 sites, around England
OL,8,Fwere rated "poor" ` failing to meet
OL,9,Feven the minimum standards for water
OL,10,Fquality, though the figure is slightly
OL,11,Fdown on the 37 bathing spots that
OL,12,Ffailed last year.
OL,14,FThe Environment Agency's testing
OL,15,Fmonitors for indicators of pollution
OL,16,Fknown to be associated with risks to
OL,17,Fbathers' health, specifically E. coli
OL,18,Fand intestinal enterococci.
