OL,7,FEach bathing water has its own
OL,8,Fpressures, and many factors can
OL,9,Finfluence bathing water quality,
OL,10,Fincluding storm overflows,
OL,11,Fagricultural runoff, birds, dogs and
OL,12,Fother local issues.
OL,14,FAlan Lovell, chair of the Environment
OL,15,FAgency, said despite the improvements,
OL,16,Fthere was more to do.
OL,18,F"The new bathing water reforms will
OL,19,Fstrengthen the way these much-loved
OL,20,Fplaces are managed," he said.
