OL,7,FAlongside the annual classifications,
OL,8,Fthe government's new Bathing Water
OL,9,FRegulation changes came into force on
OL,10,FNovember 21. These reforms are
OL,11,Fdesigned to change the 'one size fits
OL,12,Fall' approach and more closely reflect
OL,13,Fhow people use our beaches, lakes and
OL,14,Frivers.
