OL,7,FWater Minister Emma Hardy said: "Our
OL,8,Fbathing waters are at the heart of so
OL,9,Fmany communities, and these reforms
OL,10,Fwill help people experience the
OL,11,Fbenefits of our beautiful waters and
OL,12,Fconnect with nature.
OL,14,F"By ending automatic de-designation
OL,15,Fand bringing in more flexibility to
OL,16,Fwhen waters are monitored, we're
OL,17,Fcreating a system that reflects how
OL,18,Fpeople actually use their local
OL,19,Frivers, lakes and beaches.
